5. MINIMAL EVENT MODEL (APPEND-ONLY)
------------------------------------------------------------

PERSON.CREATED
PROFILE.UPDATED
AVAILABILITY.SET
DAYWORK.POSTED
DAYWORK.APPLIED
DAYWORK.REJECTED
DAYWORK.ACCEPTED
DAYWORK.CANCELLED
DAYWORK.COMPLETED
MESSAGE.SENT

All state derived from events.
No hard deletes.
No silent mutation of history.

