6. MATCH LOGIC (NO SCORING)
------------------------------------------------------------

Filtering only, not ranking.

Eligibility:
- Role match
- Cert requirements
- Location radius
- Availability overlap

Sorting:
- Most recently active
- Closest proximity
- Role-aligned tenure

No public scores.
No star ratings.
No reputation numbers.

